'''娜代日达·彼得罗维奇'''（{{lang-sr-Latn|Nadežda Petrović}}／{{lang-sr-cyr|Надежда Петровић}}；{{bd|1873年|10月12日|1915年|4月3日}}）是19世纪末20世纪初[[塞尔维亚|塞尔维亚]]重要的[[女性|女性]][[画家|画家]]、塞尔维亚[[印象派|印象派]]与[[野兽派|野兽派]]的代表人物<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Jovanov|first=Jasna M.|title=Nadezda Petrovic s obe strane objektiva.pdf|url=https://www.academia.edu/30544582|language=en|journal=|access-date=2021-01-30|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131122525/https://www.academia.edu/30544582/Nadezda_Petrovic_s_obe_strane_objektiva_pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Jovanov|first=Jasna M.|title=Photography as an (E)Vocation of the Painter. Forgotten Hobby of Nadežda Petrović|url=https://www.academia.edu/30982381|language=en|journal=|access-date=2021-01-30|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131122526/https://www.academia.edu/30982381/Photography_as_an_E_Vocation_of_the_Painter_Forgotten_Hobby_of_Nade%C5%BEda_Petrovi%C4%87|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

