=== 早年 ===
娜代日达·彼得罗维奇于1873年出生于[[塞尔维亚公国|塞尔维亚公国]][[查查克|查查克]]<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Rade|first=R. Babić|date=2008|title=Nadežda Petrović − a female painter and a nurse|url=https://scindeks-clanci.ceon.rs/data/pdf/0042-8450/2008/0042-84500810783B.pdf|journal=Istorija Medicine|volume=10|pages=1|access-date=2021-01-30|archive-date=2019-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190705001435/https://scindeks-clanci.ceon.rs/data/pdf/0042-8450/2008/0042-84500810783B.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1884年随家人移居[[贝尔格莱德|贝尔格莱德]]。而后进入当地学校接受[[高等教育|高等教育]]，于1891年毕业，1893年起担任学校[[美术|美术]]教师。1892年至1897年间，向塞尔维亚[[现实主义|现实主义]]画家{{tsl|en|Đorđe Krstić|乔尔杰·克尔斯蒂奇}}学习[[绘画|绘画]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.etrafika.net/najnovije/57974/nadezda-petrovic-heroina-zaljubljena-u-boje/|title=Nadežda Petrović: Heroina zaljubljena u boje|date=2017-12-13|website=eTrafika|language=en-US|access-date=2019-09-25|archive-date=2019-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190925175523/https://www.etrafika.net/najnovije/57974/nadezda-petrovic-heroina-zaljubljena-u-boje/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.avantartmagazin.com/nadezda-petrovic-izmedju-nerazumevanja-i-slave/|title=Nadežda Petrović, između nerazumevanja i slave|date=2014-03-27|website=Avant Art Magazin|access-date=2019-07-05|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024170839/http://www.avantartmagazin.com/nadezda-petrovic-izmedju-nerazumevanja-i-slave/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 留学慕尼黑 ===
1898年，获得塞尔维亚教育部[[奖学金|奖学金]]，前往[[慕尼黑|慕尼黑]]深造。在{{tsl|en|Anton Ažbe|安东·阿日贝}}创办的[[私立学校|私立]]绘画学校学习，并结识许多在此学习的著名[[东欧|东欧]]画家，绘画风格亦受到其影响<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Separovic|first=Ana|title=Recepcija djela Nadežde Petrović u hrvatskoj likovnoj kritici (Reception of Nadežda Petrović's Art Works in the Croatian Art Criticism)|url=https://www.academia.edu/25010408|language=en|journal=|access-date=2021-01-30|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131122605/https://www.academia.edu/25010408/Recepcija_djela_Nade%C5%BEde_Petrovi%C4%87_u_hrvatskoj_likovnoj_kritici_Reception_of_Nade%C5%BEda_Petrovi%C4%87_s_Art_Works_in_the_Croatian_Art_Criticism_|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 社会活动 ===
1900年，返回塞尔维亚，并参与各种社交活动<ref>{{Cite book|last=Miljković|first=Ljubica|date=Winter 2007|title=Nadežda Petrović|publisher=Muzej Grada Novog Sada|pages=14|isbn=978-86-7637-030-6}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.balcanicaucaso.org/bhs/zone/Srbija/Nadezda-Petrovic-slikarka-jedne-prekretnice-162587|title=Nadežda Petrović, slikarka jedne prekretnice|last=Caucaso|first=Osservatorio Balcani e|website=Osservatorio Balcani e Caucaso|language=it|access-date=2019-09-13|archive-date=2015-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150910152936/http://www.balcanicaucaso.org/bhs/zone/Srbija/Nadezda-Petrovic-slikarka-jedne-prekretnice-162587|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其首次个展于同年在[[贝尔格莱德|贝尔格莱德]]举行<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://nadezdapetrovic.rs/biografije-nadezde-petrovic/?lang=en|title=Nadežda Petrović Biography|website=Уметничка галерија Надежда Патровић Чачак|language=en-US|access-date=2019-07-14|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919191533/http://nadezdapetrovic.rs/biografije-nadezde-petrovic/?lang=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1902年，继续执教。不久后建立[[人道主义|人道主义]]组织，向受[[奥匈帝国|奥匈帝国]]压迫的塞尔维亚穷人施以援手<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.snagadobrote.com/kolo-srpskih-sestara/istorijat/|title=Istorija i tradicija {{!}} Kolo srpskih sestara Subotica|language=sr-RS|access-date=2019-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401065656/http://www.snagadobrote.com/kolo-srpskih-sestara/istorijat/|archive-date=2016-04-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.011info.com/bilo-jednom-u-beogradu/kolo-srpskih-sestara-cuvarke-tradicije-i-humanizma|title=Kolo srpskih sestara - Čuvarke tradicije i humanizma {{!}} Bilo jednom u Beogradu|website=011info - najbolji vodič kroz Beograd|language=sr|access-date=2019-09-13|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030164342/https://www.011info.com/bilo-jednom-u-beogradu/kolo-srpskih-sestara-cuvarke-tradicije-i-humanizma|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1910年至1911年，留居[[巴黎|巴黎]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://nadezdapetrovic.rs/nadezde-petrovic-sira-biografija/?lang=bs|title=Nadežda Petrović - šira biografija|website=Уметничка галерија Надежда Патровић Чачак|language=sr|access-date=2019-09-17|archive-date=2020-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918205922/http://nadezdapetrovic.rs/nadezde-petrovic-sira-biografija/?lang=bs|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Timotijević|first=Miloš|title=Милош Тимотијевић, „Политика, уметност и стварање традиција (Подизање споменика Надежди Петровић у Чачку 1955. године)” (Politics, art and creation of traditions : The establishment of Nadežda Petrović monument in Čačak in 1955)|url=https://www.academia.edu/29725557/%D0%9C%D0%B8%D0%BB%D0%BE%D1%88_%D0%A2%D0%B8%D0%BC%D0%BE%D1%82%D0%B8%D1%98%D0%B5%D0%B2%D0%B8%D1%9B_%D0%9F%D0%BE%D0%BB%D0%B8%D1%82%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D1%83%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%82%D0%BD%D0%BE%D1%81%D1%82_%D0%B8_%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B2%D0%B0%D1%80%D0%B0%D1%9A%D0%B5_%D1%82%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B4%D0%B8%D1%86%D0%B8%D1%98%D0%B0_%D0%9F%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%B8%D0%B7%D0%B0%D1%9A%D0%B5_%D1%81%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%BC%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%9D%D0%B0%D0%B4%D0%B5%D0%B6%D0%B4%D0%B8_%D0%9F%D0%B5%D1%82%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B8%D1%9B_%D1%83_%D0%A7%D0%B0%D1%87%D0%BA%D1%83_1955_%D0%B3%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B5_Politics_art_and_creation_of_traditions_The_establishment_of_Nade%C5%BEda_Petrovi%C4%87_monument_in_%C4%8Ca%C4%8Dak_in_1955_|language=en|journal=|access-date=2021-01-30|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131122437/https://www.academia.edu/29725557/%D0%9C%D0%B8%D0%BB%D0%BE%D1%88_%D0%A2%D0%B8%D0%BC%D0%BE%D1%82%D0%B8%D1%98%D0%B5%D0%B2%D0%B8%D1%9B_%D0%9F%D0%BE%D0%BB%D0%B8%D1%82%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D1%83%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%82%D0%BD%D0%BE%D1%81%D1%82_%D0%B8_%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B2%D0%B0%D1%80%D0%B0%D1%9A%D0%B5_%D1%82%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B4%D0%B8%D1%86%D0%B8%D1%98%D0%B0_%D0%9F%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%B8%D0%B7%D0%B0%D1%9A%D0%B5_%D1%81%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%BC%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%B0_%D0%9D%D0%B0%D0%B4%D0%B5%D0%B6%D0%B4%D0%B8_%D0%9F%D0%B5%D1%82%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B8%D1%9B_%D1%83_%D0%A7%D0%B0%D1%87%D0%BA%D1%83_1955_%D0%B3%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B5_Politics_art_and_creation_of_traditions_The_establishment_of_Nade%C5%BEda_Petrovi%C4%87_monument_in_%C4%8Ca%C4%8Dak_in_1955_|dead-url=no}}</ref>。曾多次在[[秋季沙龙|秋季沙龙]]中展出其画作<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Elezović|first=Zvezdana|date=2009|title=Kosovske teme paviljona Kraljevine Srbije na međunarodnoj izložbi u Rimu 1911. godine|journal=Baština|volume=27}}</ref>。

=== 巴尔干战争、第一次世界大战及其逝世 ===
1912年，因应[[巴尔干战争|巴尔干战争]]爆发，自愿成为前线[[护士|护士]]。因而被授予{{tsl|en|Order of the Red Cross (Serbia)|红十字勋章}}，以表彰其功绩<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Merenik|first=Lidija|title=Nadežda Petrović: Projekat i sudbina, Topy i Vojnoizdavački zavod, Beograd 2006|url=https://www.academia.edu/2543591|journal=Nadežda Petrović: Projekat i sudbina, Topy i Vojnoizdavački zavod, Beograd 2006|language=en|access-date=2021-01-30|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131122528/https://www.academia.edu/2543591/Nade%C5%BEda_Petrovi%C4%87_Projekat_i_sudbina_Topy_i_Vojnoizdava%C4%8Dki_zavod_Beograd_2006|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1914年7月，获悉[[奥匈帝国对塞尔维亚的最后通牒|奥匈帝国对塞尔维亚宣战]]后，立即从[[意大利|意大利]]返回贝尔格莱德，协助护理塞尔维亚军队之伤者。并因此感染[[伤寒|伤寒]]，于1915年4月3日在[[瓦列沃|瓦列沃]]逝世<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.politika.rs/scc/clanak/252672/Nadezda-Petrovic-fotograf-i-model|title=Надежда Петровић – фотограф и модел|website=Politika Online|access-date=2019-09-13|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129035259/http://www.politika.rs/scc/clanak/252672/Nadezda-Petrovic-fotograf-i-model|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

